  e.preventDefault();
  handleSignup(name, email);
}}>


  Join Now

```
- Pressing Enter in any field submits the form
- Empty fields show browser warnings
- No page reloads – smooth user experience!

**Key Takeaways**
- Wrap inputs in `` for unified submission handling
- Use `onSubmit` instead of button `onClick`
- Always prevent default to avoid page reloads

Leverage `HTML` validation attributes for quick checks

